---
title: Indian-Style Creamy Beef Rump with Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Tender beef rump is offset perfectly with a creamy tomato-based sauce in tonight’s dinner. Add a classic combination of mashed potatoes and steamed veggies to the plate to tie this dish up with a scrumptious bow.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-indian-style-creamy-beef-0a7b0186.jpg
